{"tid":1676124,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"修例風波：昨25歲仔派文宣遇襲　躁漢涉刑毀及襲擊被捕","createTime":"2019-10-26T08:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T09:11:35.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e1947436ee659c762939d1720e4439b4baacd4","tid":1676124,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"反修例風波觸發不同政見市民連番衝突！昨日(25日)下午5時許，一名25歲姓葉男子，在將軍澳澳景路88號對開一行人天橋上派發文宣，期間與一名持不同政見男子發生爭執，並遭對方用手施襲，事主的手機更被弄毀。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，葉男手部受傷，清醒由救護車送院治理。警方經初步調查後，以涉嫌刑事毀壞及普通襲擊，拘捕一名45歲姓黃男子，案件暫交由將軍澳警區反三合會行動組跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191026/bkn-20191026031810927-1026_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR1Fo6dBY2XNmwMFkVo3vZHZsP_sk9XEGi4rHWXztUoKEFFP0i-gT1GaAIc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191026%2Fbkn-20191026031810927-1026_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Fo6dBY2XNmwMFkVo3vZHZsP_sk9XEGi4rHWXztUoKEFFP0i-gT1GaAIc&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=9faba484\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191026/bkn-20191026031810927-1026_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR1Fo6dBY2XNmwMFkVo3vZHZsP_sk9XEGi4rHWXztUoKEFFP0i-gT1GaAIc</a>"},{"pid":"30fb47331f9902fcd567fbab4d4175b63c33c601","tid":1676124,"uid":138268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"依排班狗冇拉被襲嗰個拉翻啱人既情況好似多咗？想洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e82991871909562281306a885bf462d27d92eed","tid":1676124,"uid":200070,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"30fb47331f9902fcd567fbab4d4175b63c33c601","tid":1676124,"uid":138268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:01:25.000Z","msg":"依排班狗冇拉被襲嗰個拉翻啱人既情況好似多咗？想洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1